      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HAYDEN'S GIFT (4) is a well performed sprinter ideally suited at the shorter trips. Last start was fourth over 350m at Q Straight in a Grade 5 (19.49). Strike rate this distance strong having won eight of 13 tries. Form from his last run is proving strong. Looks the one to beat on his best form. BROTHER SAM (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on his swift win the start prior, getting around this track over 366m in 19.84. Has the ability and looks a key chance. CYCLONE ALFIE (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by half a length at this track in a handy 19.99. Draws out wide but has the ability and in winning form. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Has hit winning form and can measure up again. NOT THE DEPUTY (2) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.",
